Package: statquiz
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Statistics Practice in the R IDE
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Chayce", "Reed",
        email = "code.jcr@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for practicing statistics interactively inside
    your IDE. Generate randomized questions across seven topics (ANOVA,
    t-tests, correlation, probability, and more), solve them with standard
    R functions, and check your answers with immediate feedback. Includes
    a quiz mode for scored multi-question sessions and worked-solution
    explanations via explain().
